title: Meeting with ICRC officials (President of the Nagorno-Karabakh Republic)
text: ( Source : President of the Nagorno-Karabakh Republic ) On 19 October Artsakh Republic President Bako Sahakyan received Patrick Vial , newly appointed Regional Director of the International Committee of the Red Cross for Europe and Central Asia
